# PrintFlowLite Monorepo

This directory is the root of the PrintFlowLite git repository.
Each package under `packages/` is a git submodule or independent module.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Build all packages
mvn clean install -DskipTests

# Build specific package
cd packages/server
mvn clean package -DskipTests
```

## Package Directory Structure

```
PrintFlowLite/
├── pom.xml              # Root Maven POM
├── packages/
│   ├── common/          # Shared library (org.printflow.lite.common)
│   ├── core/            # Core business logic (org.printflow.lite.core)
│   ├── ext/             # Extension interface (org.printflow.lite.ext)
│   ├── server/          # Web Server (WAR)
│   ├── client/          # Desktop Client
│   ├── cups-notifier/   # CUPS Notifier (C++)
│   └── ppd/             # PostScript Printer Driver
├── MONOREPO.md          # Monorepo documentation
└── README.md            # Main project readme
```

## Version

Current version: 1.7.0
DB Schema Version: 1.10

## Tech Stack

- Java EE (JDK 8+)
- Apache Wicket
- Jetty (embedded)
- JPA / Hibernate
- Apache Derby (embedded) or PostgreSQL
- Maven
